  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Postoperative pain after Video-assisted Thoracoscopic Surgery (VAT) is still debating.
      Therefore the investigators conduct a study comparing 0.15 mg spinal morphine and control
      group in term of analgesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
